 that never returns (i.e. a promise that\nnever resolves) and when this is in the test window navigating that\nwindow causes the script to return.\n\nA simple, but not particuarly elegant, solution here is to simply\nrerun the script in the new window.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D14087", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/tools/wptrunner/wptrunner/executors/executormarionette.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "66f0ce8d3d6411977362f1c7f5dbf7615f394dea", "parents": ["15f8c7303cfb96d06492f1b450ba4ad1db9e85e4"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andrei Lazar \u003candrei.a.lazar@softvision.ro\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1501688 - Temporary files generated by opening external files with content:// scheme should be sanitized. r=JanH, a=RyanVM\n\nImplemented cache sanitizing for files generated by handling the content:// scheme.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D11779", "files": ["mobile/android/base/java/org/mozilla/gecko/BrowserApp.java", "mobile/android/modules/Sanitizer.jsm"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "e2336587275ff698b85165c571fbd6bedd77109c", "parents": ["66f0ce8d3d6411977362f1c7f5dbf7615f394dea"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Yura Zenevich \u003cyura.zenevich@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1512980 - Ensure that the right window is used when calculating the contrast ratio in accessibility highlighter. r=pbro, a=RyanVM\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D14064", "files": ["devtools/server/actors/accessibility/accessible.js", "devtools/server/actors/accessibility/walker.js", "devtools/server/actors/utils/accessibility.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "a4803c65849c00df7b2b094ed2246ff5aaf666b8", "parents": ["e2336587275ff698b85165c571fbd6bedd77109c"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Tim Nguyen \u003cntim.bugs@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1486204 - Make nsLookAndFeel.mm return transparent selection colors. r=mstange, a=RyanVM\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D8210", "files": ["layout/generic/nsTextFrame.cpp", "widget/cocoa/moz.build", "widget/cocoa/nsLookAndFeel.h", "widget/cocoa/nsLookAndFeel.mm"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "28756c341f0273bd68676aae2beda4a09e63043d", "parents": ["a4803c65849c00df7b2b094ed2246ff5aaf666b8"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Erica Wright \u003cewright@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1513076 - Do Not Track string change for Firefox 65. r=flod, a=RyanVM, l10n=flod\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D14104", "files": ["browser/components/preferences/in-content/privacy.xul", "browser/locales/en-US/browser/preferences/preferences.ftl"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "318239ee898f92d45f0cff66e7f431087c48edd1", "parents": ["28756c341f0273bd68676aae2beda4a09e63043d"], "tags": []}], "date": 1544563582, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "10319": {"changesets": [{"author": "Marco Bonardo \u003cmbonardo@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1510281 - Backed out changeset 093960021b8b because we want to use a different approach. r=mkaply, a=RyanVM\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D13328", "files": ["browser/modules/ContentSearch.jsm", "toolkit/components/places/PlacesSearchAutocompleteProvider.jsm", "toolkit/components/search/SearchSuggestionController.jsm", "toolkit/components/search/nsSearchSuggestions.js", "toolkit/components/search/tests/xpcshell/data/searchSuggestions.sjs", "toolkit/components/search/tests/xpcshell/test_searchSuggest.js", "toolkit/components/search/tests/xpcshell/test_searchSuggest_cookies.js", "toolkit/components/search/tests/xpcshell/xpcshell.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "a90f08ba09140b0990750ec622931ca8bd0fba0d", "parents": ["318239ee898f92d45f0cff66e7f431087c48edd1"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Marco Bonardo \u003cmbonardo@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1510281 - Use a private and isolated context for search suggestions. r=mkaply,Ehsan, a=RyanVM\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D13329", "files": ["toolkit/components/search/SearchSuggestionController.jsm", "toolkit/components/search/tests/xpcshell/data/searchSuggestions.sjs", "toolkit/components/search/tests/xpcshell/test_searchSuggest_cookies.js", "toolkit/components/search/tests/xpcshell/xpcshell.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "66fd4c2ab08185187eda60af2f32f82c3da325bd", "parents": ["a90f08ba09140b0990750ec622931ca8bd0fba0d"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Petru Lingurar \u003cpetru.lingurar@softvision.ro\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1497148 - Log warning for custom profile with null dir and avoid throwing exception. r=geckoview-reviewers,snorp, a=RyanVM\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D13969", "files": ["mobile/android/geckoview/src/main/java/org/mozilla/gecko/GeckoProfile.java"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "7fe309a250d8481dbe3f7238917bcc32e058486e", "parents": ["66fd4c2ab08185187eda60af2f32f82c3da325bd"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Erica Wright \u003cewright@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1513029 - Trackers and Cookie hover state colours are visible in Linux dark theme. r=ntim, a=RyanVM\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D14100", "files": ["browser/themes/linux/controlcenter/panel.css"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "100268636829cc2ed0f5618d130335f86bad6311", "parents": ["7fe309a250d8481dbe3f7238917bcc32e058486e"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jon Coppeard \u003cjcoppeard@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1510145 - Refactor GC resets and ensure the store buffer is always empty when we start sweeping. r=pbone, a=dveditz