: "Automatic version bump CLOSED TREE NO BUG a=release DONTBUILD", "files": ["browser/config/version_display.txt"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "d1674e7a6263edaf5e52a4b409afdcc54a2c1c7c", "parents": ["2a5e55f1b861e0932fc89e30e2e2c09f16c26be7"], "tags": []}], "date": 1546617111, "git_changesets": [null, null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "10446": {"changesets": [{"author": "Mozilla Releng Treescript \u003crelease+treescript@mozilla.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No bug - Tagging 35ba72605a9aba2f4d8cb9b0d024c73395b2536e with FENNEC_65_0b8_RELEASE a=release CLOSED TREE DONTBUILD", "files": [".hgtags"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "2f8a2bb753a26752c3453432b3bd74c5b79df866", "parents": ["d1674e7a6263edaf5e52a4b409afdcc54a2c1c7c"], "tags": []}], "date": 1546617286, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "10447": {"changesets": [{"author": "Mozilla Releng Treescript \u003crelease+treescript@mozilla.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No bug - Tagging 35ba72605a9aba2f4d8cb9b0d024c73395b2536e with DEVEDITION_65_0b8_RELEASE a=release CLOSED TREE DONTBUILD", "files": [".hgtags"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "8e9b7d32d8c8e94cde70b7f2046405c4e77dfbff", "parents": ["2f8a2bb753a26752c3453432b3bd74c5b79df866"], "tags": []}], "date": 1546617460, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "10448": {"changesets": [{"author": "Botond Ballo \u003cbotond@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1513232 - Avoid clamping the layout viewport size to be larger than the display size. r=kats, a=RyanVM\n\nThe clamping is intended to be a safeguard against extreme values in the\nmeta viewport tag. If the layout viewport is sized to the display size,\navoid the clamping, since the display size could legitimately be small\n(e.g. in Android 8's picture-in-picture mode).\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D15605", "files": ["dom/base/nsDocument.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "71e27c73bb26924823d74fa345a27fb243d4a0e9", "parents": ["8e9b7d32d8c8e94cde70b7f2046405c4e77dfbff"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Daosheng Mu \u003cdaoshengmu@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1514192 - Fixing Oculus Touch touch events error. r=kip, a=RyanVM\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D15589", "files": ["gfx/vr/service/OculusSession.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "3c697557546a791ba786a58478113d10f939c25c", "parents": ["71e27c73bb26924823d74fa345a27fb243d4a0e9"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andreas Pehrson \u003capehrson@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1515873 - Remove aWindowId arg from MediaManager::GetBackend. r=jib, a=RyanVM\n\nIt is unused.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D15630", "files": ["dom/media/MediaManager.cpp", "dom/media/MediaManager.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "ab6723fb0cefb88a1325ebca507dafa15e6e479a", "parents": ["3c697557546a791ba786a58478113d10f939c25c"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andreas Pehrson \u003capehrson@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1515873 - Don't create a backend as part of cleanup. r=jib, a=RyanVM\n\nThere's no guarantee a backend exists when a MediaManager does, and\ncrash-stats shows that shutdown can occur between posting a task and running\nit, making it illegal to create a backend anew.\n\nWe're safer off avoiding creating a new backend. The cleanup step we're trying\nto do is only effective if a backend already exists anyway.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D15631", "files": ["dom/media/MediaManager.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "2641666a95ba71d2fad2fcfd48bd13f8f6f0adef", "parents": ["ab6723fb0cefb88a1325ebca507dafa15e6e479a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Lars T Hansen \u003clhansen@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1516738 - Specialize x86 code generation for byte register. r=jseward, a=RyanVM", "files": ["js/src/jit-test/tests/wasm/regress/baseline-extend8.js", "js/src/wasm/WasmBaselineCompile.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "8da001054d078428a9a356caa00ce93957075aa3", "parents": ["2641666a95ba71d2fad2fcfd48bd13f8f6f0adef"], "tags": []}], "date": 1546631815, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "10449": {"changesets": [{"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Fennec l10n changesets r=release a=l10n-bump DONTBUILD\n\nes-CL -\u003e 7c9c2225cafa\nfr -\u003e 1b4d13af2a41\nnl -\u003e 5dae37bc12aa\nth -\u003e 0562c2aa0d32\ntr -\u003e 932f19cbc61d\nur -\u003e b90824896706\nvi -\u003e ebf44a6c4d1f", "files": ["mobile/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "b40748b139c2fc7f87de2ef0ddd9845ca3221211", "parents": ["8da001054d078428a9a356caa00ce93957075aa3"], "tags": []}, {"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Firefox l10n changesets r=release a=l10n-bump DONTBUILD\n\nes-CL -\u003e 7c9c2225cafa\nfr -\u003e 1b4d13af2a41\nkab -\u003e fa518784ee4e\nkk -\u003e aae5915bcfda\nnl -\u003e 5dae37bc12aa\npt-PT -\u003e 8462ebb9f058\nth -\u003e 0562c2aa0d32\ntr -\u003e 932f19cbc61d\nur -\u003e b90824896706\nvi -\u003e 7508401ad9de", "files": ["browser/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "ed823f6597eeeea6d552bcf214eb7d4952720283", "parents": ["b40748b139c2fc7f87de2ef0ddd9845ca3221211"], "tags": []}], "date": 1546632031, "git_changesets": [null, null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "10450": {"changesets": [{"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Fennec l10n changesets r=release a=l10n-bump DONTBUILD\n\nes-CL -\u003e bebf15ac2a60\npt-PT -\u003e d4167fb8e38b\nsk -\u0