serverService. r=ato a=test-only\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D16095", "files": ["testing/marionette/dom.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "888054b8eec1afea3ca6fce6dbb6a0377c11c260", "parents": ["5c04d6fccc266d49b8cd394f7c3961a68306245b"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Henrik Skupin \u003cmail@hskupin.info\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1507067 - [marionette] Add support for EventListener callback to WebElementEventTarget. r=ato a=test-only\n\nDepends on D16095\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D16096", "files": ["testing/marionette/dom.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "482eb149ad4a01dd0d192c9136d3dcd3197f4446", "parents": ["888054b8eec1afea3ca6fce6dbb6a0377c11c260"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Henrik Skupin \u003cmail@hskupin.info\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1507067 - [marionette] Listen for \"visibilitychange\" event in content process. r=ato a=test-only\n\nTo detect when the window got minimized usally \"visibilitychange\" events\nare fired to the content window. The \"WebDriver:MinimizeWindow\" command\nhas to wait for those.\n\nDepends on D16096\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D16098", "files": ["testing/marionette/driver.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "189f49635cfd710ab47ad45f24247966bed3dee1", "parents": ["482eb149ad4a01dd0d192c9136d3dcd3197f4446"], "tags": []}], "date": 1547205245, "git_changesets": [null, null, null], "user": "apavel@mozilla.com"}, "10490": {"changesets": [{"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Firefox l10n changesets r=release a=l10n-bump DONTBUILD\n\nlij -\u003e 170769eb6d61", "files": ["browser/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "7583fb564e19718bd74ad012b9d35a5aeeb629e1", "parents": ["189f49635cfd710ab47ad45f24247966bed3dee1"