empotent. r=jib, a=RyanVM\n\nDepends on D14571\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D15909", "files": ["dom/media/MediaRecorder.cpp", "dom/media/test/test_mediarecorder_state_transition.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "e74775e3a7417ae8c796cdb049d87d49805163b8", "parents": ["9e2fe8635c950031d12b391ebbc093a7921f22bc"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andreas Pehrson \u003capehrson@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1514016 - Make MediaRecorder::Pause and MediaRecorder::Resume idempotent. r=jib, a=RyanVM\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D15910", "files": ["dom/media/MediaRecorder.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "f8fa8bc2b93f37a5543c54771ca941ff8d5f953d", "parents": ["e74775e3a7417ae8c796cdb049d87d49805163b8"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Bryce Van Dyk \u003cbvandyk@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1514016 - Add WPT for MediaRecorder pause and resume behaviour. r=jib, a=RyanVM\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D14891", "files": ["testing/web-platform/meta/mediacapture-record/MediaRecorder-pause-resume.html.ini", "testing/web-platform/tests/mediacapture-record/MediaRecorder-pause-resume.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "662ea26b9f3465970dab5b0b210072076ede090e", "parents": ["f8fa8bc2b93f37a5543c54771ca941ff8d5f953d"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Bryce Van Dyk \u003cbvandyk@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1514016 - Rework MediaRecorder-stop tests to use async-await. r=jib, a=RyanVM\n\nDepends on D14891\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D14892", "files": ["testing/web-platform/meta/mediacapture-record/MediaRecorder-stop.html.ini", "testing/web-platform/tests/mediacapture-record/MediaRecorder-stop.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "f11dd983a8aa763e42fa0582058597ca32cdea43", "parents": ["662ea26b9f3465970